IAdaptable, IExecutableExtension, IMultiRosterViewPart, IPersistable, IViewPart, IWorkbenchPart, IWorkbenchPart2, IWorkbenchPart3, IWorkbenchPartOrientation
public class MultiRosterView
extends ViewPart
implements IMultiRosterViewPart

View class for displaying multiple rosters in a tree viewer. This view part implements IMultiRosterViewPart and provides the ability to display multiple rosters in a single tree viewer. This class may be subclassed as desired to add or customize behavior.

addContainer

public boolean addContainer(IContainer container)
Description copied from interface: IMultiRosterViewPart
Add container to the roster view. The container provided should adapter to the IPresenceContainerAdapter. If it does not, then false will be returned.

Specified by:
addContainer in interface IMultiRosterViewPart
Parameters:
container - The container provided should adapter to the IPresenceContainerAdapter. If it does not, then false will be returned.
Returns:
true if the given container can be added to this roster view. False if not.
